===============================================================================
Xcc - README
===============================================================================

Xcc is perl module for communicating with Mark Logic.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires libmlxcc

